Package io.github.jorgericovivas.rust_essentials.result

Record Class Ok<T,E>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
io.github.jorgericovivas.rust_essentials.result.Ok<T,E>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of result of the correct execution.
E - the type of error of a wrong execution.
Record Components:
value - the result of the correct execution.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Result<T,E>, Serializable
public record Ok<T,E>(T value) extends Record implements Result<T,E>, Serializable
Represents the result of the correct execution of an operation; Example: in a file reading, a Result could be Result<String, IOException>, where the correct execution would return Ok<String>.
